room_title: Escape room "Insert Coin(s)" by The Encrypted Escape in Green Bay
room_address: 1390 Bellevue St, Suite 105 Green Bay, WI 54311
room_description: Journey back to the 1980’s and experience the thrill of the arcade. Play some retro games, solve some bodacious puzzles, and try to win the grand prize before your time runs out and it’s game over, man! Do you have what it takes to score big in this rad room?
